Notes: Tracks 1-3: June 2, 1951
Tracks 4-7: February 17, 1951
Tracks 8-10: September 29, 1951

The June 2 and September 29 broadcasts from Birdland have appeared over the years on a variety of bootlegs. The February 17 is made available for the first time anywhere. The source for this material was discs cut from the original broadcasts and the fidelity is primitve. Every effort has been made to obtain the best possible sound for this historic music.
